text: Ðis synd ða landgemæro ðe gebyriað into Codestune.
Of Gytinges æwylme on norðdene on ðone grenan weg.
Of ðæm haran stane andlang grenan weges on scepe clif.
Andlang scepe clifes in on meos mære.
Of meos mære andlang dene on geolowonford.
Ondlang þristlongan dene to brocces slæde.
Of brocces slæde ondlong ecge ðæt on ða twegen þornas.
Of ðæm twam þornan on wadbeorh.
Of lafercan beorhge a bi ðam æcra heafdan ðæt on scyttanfæn.
Ondlang ðæt eft on Gytinges æwylm.
Æðelmund and Wulfhelm and ælfnoð and Godwine.
